(1) Create New Folder 

    myapp > templates

(2) Register templates Folder

    djangoapp > djangoapp > settings.py > TEMPLATES > DIRS

    [os.path.join(BASE_DIR,'templates')]

===================

(1) templates > 1_index_template.html

(2) template loading

    myapp > views_template.py

(3) * urls.py register

    path('template/', views_template.index)

===================

variable   - {{ }} 

tags       - {%  %}
  
{% csrf_token %} - Cross Site Request Forgeries
{% block %}      - can be overridden by child templates
{% extends %}    - template extends a parent template
{% include %}    - including other templates within a template

{% for %} {% endfor %} - looping

{% if %} {% endif %}   - condition